text.tspan: Two microphones required, SM81 or KM 184 or similar
first pointed towards guitar sound hole
Microphones routed to an interface - ex. Scarlett 2i2
USB from interface to personal computer
Computer sends HDMI (video only) to television or projector
Computer sends processed live audio and samples back to the interface
Interface output is sent to house mix
Optionally, I would like to monitor the house mix with an in-ear monitor
This is not pictured above, but it may be useful to send the pre-processed
microphone sends to the house mix as well. They may not be needed,
